text: Compulsion is a 1959 American crime drama movie directed by Richard Fleischer and based on the 1956 novel of the same name by Meyer Levin. It stars Orson Welles, Dean Stockwell, Diane Varsi, E. G. Marshall, Bradford Dillman, Martin Milner, Edward Binns and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1959 crime movies Category:1959 drama movies Category:1950s crime drama movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Richard Fleischer
